com.google.publicalerts.cap

Class Reasons

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.publicalerts.cap.Reasons
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Reason>

    public final class Reasons
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Reason>
    A simple collection of Reason objects. The content is indexed to allow for fast lookups based on the reasons' levels.

    Insertion order is not preserved, duplicate objects are not overwritten.

    This class is immutable and thread-safe.
